= Introduction

This document is an example on how to use the template. The following chapters mark out some specialties of the template and Typst.

You can have a look at every concept by reading the explanation comments or read the source code on #link("https://github.com/dhbw-typst/oderso-template")[GitHub]. You will not need every concept explained, so do not despair if you do not understand everything.

If you have any questions, don’t hesitate to reach out to the maintainers of this template or create an issue.
